description:
by singedsun

She barely gives thought to the lyrics, adding song that resonate almost as soon as she realizes her thoughts have drifted back to Villanelle.

Maybe if there’s enough of them a pattern will emerge. Maybe they hold a key to understanding Villanelle. More often than she listens to the list, she is scrolling through it as if they might hold a clue to her own subconscious. Maybe they don’t hold the key to Villanelle, but to herself.

body:
This week on #QueerBeats, @glaad announced their media award nominees, #TCA19 brought lots of good queer news, and we finally got some new info about The L Word reboot!

Welcome back to Queer Beats, your weekly one-stop shop for queer television news! This week, GLAAD announced their media award nominees, the TCAs brought lots of good queer news, and we finally got some new info about The L Word reboot!

GLAAD Awards
